WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.429 --> 00:00:01.474
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.474 --> 00:00:02.520
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.520 --> 00:00:03.370
Day 52.

00:00:03.795 --> 00:00:06.374
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:07.739 --> 00:00:09.559
Last night was amazing.

00:00:09.559 --> 00:00:14.650
We went to that Billy Burke meeting, and there were so many of you who came to support him.

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:16.542
I'm excited that you all came.

00:00:16.542 --> 00:00:17.657
That was awesome.

00:00:17.657 --> 00:00:44.453
People drove from Mexico City; I saw a family there that drove almost a 23 or 24-hour drive—all day, all night kind of a deal.

00:00:44.453 --> 00:00:54.093
People are hungry; they're hungry for an authentic move of God.

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:05.799
I met a man—I don't remember his name, but there's something about him.

00:01:05.799 --> 00:01:25.262
He had a green shirt on with yellow letters and he had a bald head, and his wife was blonde-headed.

00:01:25.262 --> 00:01:57.279
The Lord was speaking to me that there's a call on this man's life, and there's going to be a lot more the Lord's going to do with him.

00:02:01.387 --> 00:02:05.382
I thought about you all night when I came home.

00:02:05.382 --> 00:02:30.017
The Lord has His hand on you, sir, and there's going to be a lot more that God's going to do with you and your family.

00:02:31.062 --> 00:03:06.933
There's going to be some more knitting together in your marriage and things with your wife, and there's going to be a great wave that's going to come on you over the next year or so.

00:03:06.933 --> 00:03:25.066
I'm telling you, God has His hand on you, and I could sense it very strongly whenever I was standing there.

00:03:29.336 --> 00:03:47.680
I'm a very introverted person, so it's very awkward when so many people want to say hi, and I'm not used to that.

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:56.453
Whenever I'm going around folks, I'm discerning people instantaneously.

00:03:56.453 --> 00:04:34.759
I told you all my gift; whenever I go around people, I'm reading, and the Lord's allowing me to see things and bringing in so much information and data.

00:04:51.660 --> 00:05:01.232
It's overwhelming sometimes, and I get to the point where I go, 'Okay, I've got to go home now.

00:05:01.232 --> 00:05:15.800
' So I'm sorry if I didn't get to talk to everybody.

00:05:17.899 --> 00:05:44.053
I know there were a lot of people that wanted to say hi, and I appreciate you driving so far.

00:05:44.053 --> 00:06:01.850
It was all about Jesus, and it was so exciting to see you there.

00:06:01.850 --> 00:06:14.868
My family loved it; it was a blessing.

00:06:14.868 --> 00:06:27.055
Thank you for coming and supporting Brother Billy.

00:06:27.055 --> 00:06:50.387
He is an amazing man of God, and we're excited that we got to be a part of that meeting.

00:06:58.349 --> 00:07:04.190
There are two more days of meetings: Monday, which is tonight, and Tuesday.

00:07:04.190 --> 00:07:34.046
If you need healing and deliverance—there was one man who had chronic hiccuping, and I saw the fire of God all over him.

00:07:43.111 --> 00:07:54.061
I believe he got delivered from that; that was a demonic attachment, and the Lord set him free.

00:07:58.840 --> 00:08:13.263
I believe with all my heart he got his miracle last night.

00:08:13.263 --> 00:08:28.235
Like I said, there were so many of you that got a miracle.

00:08:29.080 --> 00:08:47.258
There was a lady that had ovarian cancer who got set free.

00:08:47.258 --> 00:09:03.114
I saw the fire of God hit her.

00:09:03.114 --> 00:09:29.120
She was a rhema graduate, and the Lord is going to do some major things with her in her ministry.

00:09:32.109 --> 00:09:38.543
The Lord's not done with her.

00:09:38.543 --> 00:09:53.239
It was exciting to be a part of it.

00:09:53.239 --> 00:09:58.346
Praise the Lord.

00:10:01.685 --> 00:10:07.380
I'm excited you're all here today.

00:10:07.380 --> 00:10:19.947
We'll see what happens tonight and on Tuesday night.

00:10:19.947 --> 00:10:36.676
I'm just glad to be a part of such an amazing meeting.

00:10:36.676 --> 00:10:49.020
If he comes to your area, don't miss out on it.

00:10:49.020 --> 00:11:07.173
I'm telling you, the spirit of the Lord moves mightily in these meetings.

00:11:07.173 --> 00:11:32.560
I think what I've come to figure out is: is it Billy Burke, is it healing virtue?

00:11:32.560 --> 00:11:35.245
It's expectation.

00:11:35.245 --> 00:11:48.509
It's about Jesus and expecting Jesus to do something mightily in your life.

00:11:48.509 --> 00:12:08.880
Expectation brings the manifestation, and it pulls on the anointing that's on that individual.

00:12:08.880 --> 00:13:12.199
When you're expecting God to move mightily in a service, if you just go with your hands folded and you're just watching like, 'Well, let's just see what Jesus does,' and your attitude is like that, you can take it to the bank—you're probably not going to get anything because your attitude is already stinky.

00:13:12.199 --> 00:13:43.595
If you go with that anticipation that 'I am coming to touch the hem of the Master's garment today,' expectation brings the manifestation of what you're believing for.

00:13:49.925 --> 00:13:57.533
I believe with all my heart it's that childlike faith.

00:13:58.100 --> 00:14:23.870
I heard one person say, 'Even the dogs eat the crumbs off the Master's table,' just like what that lady said in the Bible.

00:14:23.870 --> 00:14:45.854
Lord, I know I'm a child, but even the dogs get the crumbs off the Master's table.

00:15:00.516 --> 00:15:04.849
I am so desperate for an authentic move of the Spirit of the Lord in these last days.

00:15:04.849 --> 00:15:46.908
I know beyond a shadow of a doubt that there's a great harvest of souls beyond anyone's comprehension that's about to take place, with healings, demonstrations, and manifestations of the glory.

00:15:46.908 --> 00:16:02.245
I believe this is the time that we're going to see some amazing things.

00:16:02.245 --> 00:16:24.977
If you have expectation in an atmosphere like that, you'll receive what God has for you.

00:16:34.502 --> 00:16:50.570
For those who say, 'I can't make it to that in the Spirit atmosphere,' we receive it today on the camera.

00:16:50.570 --> 00:17:06.200
Nothing is impossible to those who believe; all things are possible.

00:17:06.200 --> 00:17:30.786
Today you're going to receive your healing, your manifestation of what you're believing for—finances, deliverance, whatever it may be.

00:17:30.786 --> 00:17:38.605
Nothing's too big and nothing's too small.

00:17:42.126 --> 00:17:57.660
I saw people last night—one had a rod in her back from a major accident or surgery.

00:17:57.660 --> 00:18:13.480
Pastor Billy laid hands on her, and the power of God went into her.

00:18:13.480 --> 00:18:40.424
He said the Lord told him He's taking that rod out of there by a supernatural creative miracle.

00:18:40.424 --> 00:18:57.148
Her husband touched her spine to see and said, 'I don't feel it.

00:18:57.148 --> 00:19:05.240
' Her husband validated the miracle right there.

00:19:18.428 --> 00:19:18.862
I believe she's healed today.

00:19:18.862 --> 00:19:30.986
It takes a supernatural something to take a rod out of somebody's back.

00:19:30.986 --> 00:19:40.510
Ladies and gentlemen, it's time to believe God for the impossible.

00:19:40.510 --> 00:19:56.520
It's time to believe God even for my Megan, that she's fully healed and whole.

00:19:57.760 --> 00:20:09.960
There will be a day when Megan's on here telling you how big her God is.

00:20:09.960 --> 00:20:16.679
Jesus is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:20:16.679 --> 00:20:37.331
Yesterday when I was praying, I saw a suitcase bomb in Syria, I believe in Damascus.

00:20:41.017 --> 00:21:16.840
I found out that Assad left and he fled the country to Moscow to get away because the rebels took it over.

00:21:16.840 --> 00:21:55.120
There were big-time weapons in Syria, and the Lord showed me yesterday that this thing was going to escalate into the Ezekiel 38 and 39 war, the Gog and Magog stuff.

00:21:55.120 --> 00:22:16.531
We are on the edge of a major thing happening in Israel and the Middle East.

00:22:16.531 --> 00:22:35.942
Jesus told us there would be wars and rumors of wars before He came back.

00:22:37.769 --> 00:22:39.960
We're there, folks.

00:22:40.726 --> 00:23:01.467
We're seeing the signs of the times, watching the fruit on the fig tree.

00:23:01.467 --> 00:23:24.874
Looking at where it all started in the Middle East, we're going back to the foundation of things.

00:23:24.874 --> 00:23:32.039
Jesus is coming, and people are still asleep.

00:23:33.039 --> 00:23:56.440
We get distracted by shiny things, by materialism, or the issues we go through, but we have to shake ourselves awake.

00:23:56.440 --> 00:24:08.821
We're going to see an escalation of things like never before.

00:24:12.049 --> 00:24:42.585
The Lord said we have been focused on politics, the economy, and war, but there is another side we've not seen: signs in the heavens.

00:24:42.585 --> 00:24:57.280
Look at the drones being seen over New Jersey and all this weirdness.

00:24:57.280 --> 00:25:15.413
I told you they would start to talk about fallen angels and aliens.

00:25:15.413 --> 00:25:25.171
Is that part of this Nephilim stuff?

00:25:42.886 --> 00:25:46.730
I have no idea; it could be false flag weirdness or someone playing in their garage.

00:25:52.279 --> 00:26:29.1000
All I know is we're about to see some crazy stuff because there has to be a great deception to try to snare everybody when the Rapture of the church takes place.

00:26:29.1000 --> 00:26:45.430
How will they explain away hundreds of millions, if not billions, of people disappearing overnight?

00:26:52.190 --> 00:27:08.660
It's going to crash the economy and cause worldwide panic in the twinkling of an eye.

00:27:08.660 --> 00:27:19.360
Mothers will be frantically looking for their children.

00:27:19.360 --> 00:27:31.079
They have to have something to explain the mass chaos.

00:27:31.079 --> 00:27:39.173
Satan knows that Jesus is coming soon.

00:27:39.173 --> 00:27:54.194
Nobody knows the day or the hour, but He didn't say we wouldn't know the signs.

00:27:55.765 --> 00:28:13.708
I believe a true believer is going to have that inward knowing that we are getting really close.

00:28:16.929 --> 00:28:33.244
You say it could be four years, but look how fast 2024 has gone.

00:28:37.960 --> 00:28:48.900
We are less than two weeks away from the end of the year.

00:28:48.900 --> 00:29:06.233
If we have four or five more years left, think about how fast that is.

00:29:06.233 --> 00:29:19.256
A great supernatural wealth transfer is going to begin in 2025.

00:29:19.256 --> 00:29:28.809
You can see the rockets starting to lift off.

00:29:36.360 --> 00:29:46.645
There are things changing right now, like a floodgate getting ready to be released.

00:29:46.645 --> 00:30:05.573
I believe the button will be President Trump being inaugurated into office.

00:30:05.573 --> 00:30:36.779
I saw a dam full of sludge being held back, but the Lord said He's giving us a window through the prayers of the saints.

00:30:36.779 --> 00:30:44.240
What will you do with this window?

00:30:44.480 --> 00:31:00.000
We have a sliver of time for revival, to get our stuff in order.

00:31:00.000 --> 00:31:15.279
Yes, we'll see an economic crisis, drought, earthquakes, volcanoes, and asteroids.

00:31:15.279 --> 00:31:23.725
It's coming like a freight train.

00:31:28.990 --> 00:31:30.440
The Earth is in anticipation.

00:31:32.280 --> 00:31:38.136
The cup of sin is full.

00:31:38.136 --> 00:32:01.316
It's time to get your heart right with Jesus, to repent and walk in holiness.

00:32:01.316 --> 00:32:16.130
Get Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 inside your heart.

00:32:16.130 --> 00:32:36.360
Have a revelation of who you are in Christ, knowing you have authority over the devil to tread on serpents and scorpions.

00:32:36.360 --> 00:32:47.559
I pray every day that our eyes are flooded with light.

00:32:51.810 --> 00:32:55.930
We're hungry for more of You, Father.

00:32:55.930 --> 00:33:05.510
We want to go from glory to glory.

00:33:05.510 --> 00:33:11.099
It's time to get serious.

00:33:11.099 --> 00:33:20.940
We're going to see some radical stuff in 2025.

00:33:20.940 --> 00:33:39.479
I heard a lady tell Diana that her daughter, whom we've been praying for, is having twins.

00:33:39.479 --> 00:33:57.264
If you're believing for children today, believe that the fruit of your womb is blessed.

00:33:57.264 --> 00:34:11.879
We take authority over the spirit of anxiety and miscarriage.

00:34:15.352 --> 00:34:39.405
In the name of Jesus, we believe every one of you will have a full-term baby with nothing missing and nothing broken.

00:34:39.405 --> 00:34:45.580
Your children will be blessed.

00:34:45.580 --> 00:34:52.811
Cast your care onto the Father.

00:34:52.811 --> 00:35:37.341
We're going to see some things around us, and if you're not in the right place, you may have the opportunity to go home early, but I believe there's divine protection for you.

00:35:37.341 --> 00:36:01.314
It's not a time to fear; it's a time to pray and rise up.

00:36:01.314 --> 00:36:40.680
We're not going to be freaked out about the suitcase thing; we're going to pray over it and the escalation in the Middle East and Ukraine.

00:36:40.680 --> 00:36:48.319
We see the rocket ship liftoff.

00:36:49.417 --> 00:36:55.000
Father, I thank You for Your supernatural hand on these people.

00:37:04.342 --> 00:37:05.319
You are the miracle worker.

00:37:05.319 --> 00:37:16.970
Today is the day for their manifestation.

00:37:20.050 --> 00:37:29.280
I thank You for finances, creative ideas to get wealth, and supernatural favor.

00:37:29.280 --> 00:37:57.557
Everything we touch has favor because You dwell inside of us.

00:38:20.469 --> 00:38:22.840
We serve a God of more than enough.

00:38:26.154 --> 00:38:43.947
We are not going to shrink back; we're going to take the ground.

00:38:43.947 --> 00:39:06.280
We call the walls of Jericho to come down over your household.

00:39:25.497 --> 00:39:29.107
We give a shout of praise to the Lord.

00:39:29.107 --> 00:39:51.150
We break the back of lack and believe for a hundredfold return.

00:40:01.685 --> 00:40:21.655
This is the time to be the head and not the tail, to have witty ideas and excel.

00:40:21.655 --> 00:40:38.729
We're taking back the spiritual land that the enemy stole.

00:40:41.040 --> 00:41:03.240
Father, we will minister the truth in love—the meat of the word, like T-bone steaks, not some porridge milky message.

00:41:24.100 --> 00:41:24.450
Come up higher to the throne room to prophesy.

00:41:24.450 --> 00:41:34.031
It's time to soar on wings like eagles.

00:41:35.560 --> 00:41:55.753
We thank You for healing from cancer, diabetes, and heart disease.

00:41:56.226 --> 00:42:08.332
We pray over the Trump administration and his protection today.

00:42:08.332 --> 00:42:20.700
We thank You for Solomon's wisdom for him.

00:42:20.700 --> 00:42:41.533
I pray over Elon Musk and thank You that he and Trump are born again.

00:42:41.533 --> 00:42:55.289
We take authority over the blinders of the enemy.

00:42:55.289 --> 00:43:16.160
We plead the blood of Jesus over Elon Musk and thank You that Starlink will be used to spread the gospel.

00:43:25.142 --> 00:43:29.217
It is the goodness of God that draws men to repentance.

00:43:29.217 --> 00:43:35.800
We want what they have—healing, deliverance, and manifestations.

00:43:43.319 --> 00:43:45.314
We are the clay, and He is the Potter.

00:43:45.314 --> 00:43:47.235
Anoint us with the fire of the Holy Spirit.

00:43:47.235 --> 00:43:53.405
Even our shadows should touch people and heal them.

00:43:53.405 --> 00:47:08.430
People will turn from their wicked ways.

00:47:08.440 --> 00:47:48.731
We lift up Canada and thank You that Justin Trudeau is removed and a godly leader comes forth.

00:47:48.731 --> 00:48:03.706
We pray for godly leaders throughout the EU, Germany, Finland, Ireland, and Italy.

00:48:13.200 --> 00:48:33.840
I thank You for the warning regarding the volcano I saw in Italy by Rome; I thank You that believers would hear and get out of harm's way.

00:48:33.840 --> 00:48:44.469
We call for revival in South Korea and all of Asia.

00:48:44.469 --> 00:49:02.813
Something is going on in South Korea; there's going to be a stirring in the government and the church.

00:49:10.400 --> 00:49:10.725
The Asian people are not forgotten.

00:49:10.725 --> 00:49:22.660
We call for a major move of God among Latinos and the Spanish communities.

00:50:02.223 --> 00:50:24.970
We thank You that false religion would fall off.

00:50:24.970 --> 00:53:10.596
