00:58:45.012 --> 00:59:10.360
People are desperate for financial liberty.

00:59:11.600 --> 00:59:18.990
The only thing that brings happiness is Jesus.

00:59:18.990 --> 01:00:13.057
We thank You for the truth throughout the Latino communities and Cuba.

01:00:17.143 --> 01:01:04.034
We thank You that the strongholds of evil dictators are coming down.

01:01:19.705 --> 01:01:37.507
We take authority over the witchcraft I'm seeing in Cuba: Santería.

01:01:37.507 --> 01:01:48.613
It's a demonic stronghold, so we pronounce freedom.

01:01:48.613 --> 01:02:11.855
Raise up leaders in Cuba like David, with no fear.

01:03:16.500 --> 01:03:24.839
The cult tries to be bullies like the mafia.

01:03:24.839 --> 01:03:34.983
I pray over Jamaica, the Bahamas, and all the islands.

01:03:34.983 --> 01:03:48.418
Raise up great fire to set the people free.

01:03:48.418 --> 01:04:08.255
I thank You for Africa and the freedom coming there from witchcraft.

01:04:08.255 --> 01:04:30.560
I saw a crow's hand with blood on a stick; we thank You that those people are free from witch doctors.

01:04:30.560 --> 01:05:03.368
Raise up people with an anointing to raise the dead and heal the blind.

01:05:03.368 --> 01:05:19.831
We call forth the great warriors and harvesters.

01:05:19.831 --> 01:05:23.417
I worship You, Father.

01:05:23.417 --> 01:05:34.845
We rejoice and are glad.

01:05:34.845 --> 01:06:03.670
Holy Spirit, flood this place.

01:06:03.680 --> 01:06:36.629
We're desperate and thirsty for You.

01:06:36.629 --> 01:06:51.000
Fresh living water flows from Your throne today.

01:06:51.000 --> 01:07:00.186
I'm going to pray in the spirit now.

01:07:00.186 --> 01:07:24.435
This is a perfect prayer from my spirit to the Father.

01:07:24.435 --> 01:07:56.844
Don't speak against the Holy Spirit; keep your mouth quiet if you don't understand it, because I'm concerned for your safety.

01:07:56.844 --> 01:08:04.383
We yield to the Holy Spirit.

01:08:04.383 --> 01:08:31.248
Sometimes praying in tongues feels dry, like you're in a desert, but you have to push through the dryness to hit a gusher.

01:08:31.853 --> 01:08:36.340
You don't put a time on it.

01:08:38.827 --> 01:08:42.494
You push past your flesh to see the breakthroughs.

01:08:42.494 --> 01:09:04.448
I bind hindering spirits in the name of Jesus and command you to cease and desist.

01:09:04.448 --> 01:09:24.299
Blessed are the pure in heart, for they will see God.

01:09:35.639 --> 01:10:01.880
The atmosphere is changing; it's going into the river.

01:10:03.992 --> 01:10:15.690
The glory is here.

01:10:15.690 --> 01:10:25.300
We sit at Your feet, Papa.

01:10:29.777 --> 01:10:43.060
I thank You for boldness where there has been timidity.

01:10:43.060 --> 01:10:53.650
Rise up and be bold as a lion.

01:10:53.650 --> 01:11:19.920
We call the people in from the north, south, east, and west to this channel.

01:11:19.920 --> 01:11:40.030
We call in the laborers and the million-person prayer army that will change the nations.

01:11:40.030 --> 01:11:49.859
Show them the way here, Holy Spirit.

01:11:49.859 --> 01:11:54.297
It's all about Jesus.

01:11:54.297 --> 01:12:00.860
We thank You for Your angels.

01:12:00.860 --> 01:12:12.505
We command those rats nipping at people's heels to be gone.

01:12:12.505 --> 01:12:34.679
There are levels of the glory and anointing—ankle deep, knee deep, waist deep, and over the head.

01:12:34.679 --> 01:12:46.830
Each level is by the refiner's fire.

01:12:46.830 --> 01:12:58.739
It's less of you and more of Him.

01:12:58.739 --> 01:13:15.360
The refiner's fire burns out your weaknesses, whether it's finances, addictions, pride, or lust.

01:13:15.360 --> 01:13:30.080
Clean out your closet and let the Holy Spirit change you into a kingly anointing.

01:13:30.080 --> 01:13:37.360
It's about dying to self daily.

01:13:37.360 --> 01:13:49.674
Create in me a clean heart and take out the chaff.

01:13:49.674 --> 01:13:56.235
Don't be a religious Pharisee.

01:13:56.235 --> 01:14:06.929
Come to Him like a child.

01:14:24.399 --> 01:14:31.251
I met a man yesterday who couldn't read or write; that person has a great opportunity because they're desperate.

01:14:31.251 --> 01:14:51.840
My own spelling is atrocious, but I do not allow that to be a crutch.

01:15:08.190 --> 01:15:08.485
I refuse to have a victim mentality.

01:15:08.485 --> 01:15:15.124
Rise up and slay the giant.

01:15:15.124 --> 01:15:17.880
God doesn't need you to have a PhD to use you.

01:15:17.880 --> 01:15:24.325
Thank you for joining me.

01:15:24.325 --> 01:15:37.913
Those who stick around are the ones who are hungry.

01:15:37.913 --> 01:15:47.020
It's a slow cooker, not a microwave.

01:15:47.020 --> 01:15:50.999
Pushing in is what changes you.

01:15:50.999 --> 01:15:56.360
I hope this video blessed you.

01:15:56.360 --> 01:16:03.290
If you're new, please subscribe.

01:16:03.290 --> 01:16:19.697
2025 is going to be an amazing year for accuracy in the prophetic.

01:16:23.280 --> 01:16:30.400
You have to go deep to get the true words.

01:16:30.400 --> 01:16:34.984
Like, subscribe, and comment.

01:16:34.984 --> 01:16:39.182
We'll see you tomorrow.

01:16:45.462 --> 01:16:46.251
God bless you.

01:16:49.520 --> 01:16:50.760
Bye-bye.
